---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Articles & Reflections — Verdandi Weaver
description: Spacious essays for slow reading. Nervous systems, awakening, emotional ecology, and the long way home.
permalink: /articles.html
---

<section class="hero container fade-up">
  <p class="t-eyebrow hero__eyebrow">Reading</p>
  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">Articles &amp; reflections</h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">Spacious essays for slow reading. Nervous systems, awakening, emotional ecology, and the long way home.</p>
</section>

<section class="section fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    {% set articles = collections.articles | sort(true, false, "data.date") %}
    {% if articles.length %}
      <div class="stack-lg">
        {% for article in articles %}
        <article class="card card--quiet">
          <div class="card__body">
            {% if article.data.date %}<p class="t-meta">{{ article.data.date | date("DD MMMM YYYY") }}</p>{% endif %}
            <h2 class="t-h3">{{ article.data.title }}</h2>
            {% if article.data.description %}<p class="t-body t-pretty">{{ article.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
            <a class="link-chev" href="{{ article.url }}">Read →</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="container narrow center-text">
        <p class="t-lead t-pretty">Essays and reflections are being written. They will arrive slowly.</p>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
